snippet.title: Marie Claire
snippet.description:
Welcome to Marie Claire! We love beauty, skincare, fashion, books, pop culture and, of course, talking about it all with our favorite celebrities. 

We've got fresh content for you every week, with series like Masked and Answered, Shelf Portrait, Precious Metals and Pop Quiz, plus a mix of can't-miss critical stories. Make sure to subscribe to keep up with the latest: http://bit.ly/SUBSCRIBEtoMARIECLAIRE

We want our channel to be a safe place for our talent and our audience. Your comments are always welcome, even if they are critiques. However, we will delete your remarks if they are deemed off-topic, contain vulgar language, or are disrespectful of others.
